Text: Can you get pregnant from precum?

You can get pregnant any time you have sex. If sperm gets inside the vagina, it’s possible to get pregnant. And both pre cum and semen (cum) carry sperm. This means you need to be using a condom the WHOLE time you’re having sex. If you wait until things are getting hot and heavy towards the end, it’s too late!
